        "title": "An assessment methodology for tunnelling beneath bridges considering soil–structure interaction",
        "published": "2026-06-08",
        "url": "https://doi.org/10.1016/j.tust.2026.107810",
        "authors": [
          "Eugene K.L. Wong",
