        "title": "The Role of Stress Heterogeneity in Seismic Slip Revealed Through Experiments on Laboratory Faults",
        "published": "2026-06-09",
        "url": "https://doi.org/10.1007/s00603-026-05663-0",
        "authors": [
          "Shupeng Chai",
